    {"id":"keys-text","type":"text","x":785,"y":300,"width":520,"height":235,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#155e75","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"index":"a9","roundness":null,"seed":10,"version":1,"versionNonce":10,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":0,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"DATA EXPLORER                         [Refresh]\nFilter keys:  user:*________________\n\nKEY                 TYPE      TTL      VALUE\nuser:1              string    24s      Matty\nuser:2              string    ∞        Ada\nsession:abc         hash      45m      3 fields\nqueue:emails        list      ∞        2 items\n\nSelect a key → inspect its value, TTL, encoding,\nand commands that recently changed it.","fontSize":18,"fontFamily":3,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"DATA EXPLORER                         [Refresh]\nFilter keys:  user:*________________\n\nKEY                 TYPE      TTL      VALUE\nuser:1              string    24s      Matty\nuser:2              string    ∞        Ada\nsession:abc         hash      45m      3 fields\nqueue:emails        list      ∞        2 items\n\nSelect a key → inspect its value, TTL, encoding,\nand commands that recently changed it.","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},
